quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Function Return[/h1]

Another example: [code format="js" codeId="681"]function addNumbers(a, b) {
   var c = a+b;
   [b]return c;[/b]
}
document.write( addNumbers(40, 2) );
//Outputs 42[/code]
[note]The document.write command outputs the value returned by the function, which is the sum of the two parameters.[/note]
